### 1.故事的开始
公司的运营后台管理系统有很多弹窗查询，查询结果显示在表格的页面，因此想抽出一个组件。公司使用的是element-ui库，于是就基于ui库封装了组件

![avatar][tableTypes]

### 2.组件传入变量分析
从上述三张图片可以看出，需要抽离的变量有：
+ 1.弹窗是否显示：boolean类型
+ 2.弹窗宽度：字符串带单位（如640px）
+ 3.列表接口：即列表获取数据的接口
+ 4.接口请求方式
+ 5.弹窗标题：字符串
+ 6.搜索条件（可以有多个）：所以该变量应为数组类型
+ 7.搜索
+ 8.列表对应字段
+ 9.已选中内容
+ 10.对应的key值
+ 11.搜索按钮样式
+ 12.表格单选还是多选(单选需求为后续扩充)
+ 13.单选时的值

### 3.定义组件变量
#### 1.父组件传入变量
由于变量过多，因此将变量全部作为对象函数multiSelectBounced的返回值
```javascript
props:{
    multiSelectBounced:{
      type:Object,
      default:() => {
        return {
          // 是否显示
          show:false,
          // 弹框宽度
          width:'640px',
          // 列表接口
          listUrl:'',
          // 接口请求方式
          method:'get',
          // 标题
          title:'',
          // 搜索条件
          search:[{
            label:'',
            value:'',
            // 隐藏
            isHidden:false,
            style:'',
            // 1-输入框2-下拉框
            type:'',
            // 下拉框时的option
            options:[]
          }],
          // 搜索(必传)
          searchData:{},
          // 列表对应字段(type:1(数组转字符串)stringValue:'字符串转数组所用的字段')
          tableFields:[{
            label:'',
            value:''
          }],
          // 已选中内容{id:'1',name:'测试'}
          changeIdsArr:[],
          // 对应的key值 {id:'id',name:'name'content:'content',total:'total'}
          changeArrKey:{
            id:'id',
            name:'name',
            resultList:'resultList',
            records:'records'
          },
          // 搜索按钮样式
          searchBtnStyle:'margin-left:140px',
          // 表格单选多选，0-多选，1-单选  ps:该字段由体检报告录入需求扩充
          checkType: 0,
          radioValue: ''
        }
      }
    }
  }
```
#### 2.组件中的变量
```javascript
  data () {
    return {
      loading:true,
      list:[],
      page:1,
      total:10,
      changeRow:[],
      multiSelectData:{},
      // 搜索条件
      searchData:{}
    }
  }
```

### 4.主要代码模块
#### 1.html结构
```html
  <div class="multi-select-bounced">
    <el-dialog
      :title="multiSelectBounced.title"
      :visible.sync="multiSelectBounced.show"
      :width="multiSelectBounced.width||'640px'"
      :close-on-click-modal="false"
      >
      <!-- 条件筛选 start -->
      <div>
        <ul class="filters-sec" v-if="multiSelectBounced.search&&multiSelectBounced.search.length>0">
          <li>
            <div class="filters-sec-wrap">
              <div v-for="(item,index) in multiSelectBounced.search" :key="index" >
                <div class="filters-sec-span" v-if="!item.isHidden">
                  <span v-if="item.label">{{item.label}}：</span>
                  <el-input v-if="item.type==1||!item.type" v-model.trim="searchData[item.value]" :placeholder="item.placeholder" :style="item.style?item.style:'width:300px'" clearable></el-input>
                  <el-select v-if="item.type==2" v-model="searchData[item.value]" :placeholder="item.placeholder" :style="item.style?item.style:'width:300px'" clearable>
                    <el-option
                      v-for="item in item.options"
                      :key="item.value"
                      :label="item.label"
                      :value="item.value">
                    </el-option>
                  </el-select>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="multi-select-bounced-btn" :style="multiSelectBounced.searchBtnStyle?multiSelectBounced.searchBtnStyle:'margin-left:140px'">
                <div @click="search()" class="primary-btn mr10">查询</div>
                <div @click="reset()" class="info-btn">重置</div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </li>
        </ul>
        <!-- 条件筛选 end -->

        <!-- 主列表 start -->
        <el-table :data="list" style="margin-top:20px;min-height:192px" v-loading="loading" border @select="handleSelectionChange" @select-all="handleSelectionChange" ref="multipleTable">
          <el-table-column width="50" align="center" v-if="multiSelectBounced.checkType === 1">
            <template slot-scope="scope">
              <el-radio v-model="multiSelectBounced.radioValue" :label="scope.row.id" align="right" @change="radioChange(scope.row)">&nbsp;</el-radio>
            </template>
          </el-table-column>
          <el-table-column type="selection" width="50" align="center" v-if="multiSelectBounced.checkType !== 1"></el-table-column>
          <el-table-column  v-for="(item,index) in multiSelectBounced.tableFields" :prop="item['value']" :label="item['label']" align="center" :key="index" show-overflow-tooltip>
            <template slot-scope="scope">
                <div v-if="item['type']!=1">
                  {{scope.row[item['value']]}}
                </div>
                <div v-if="item['type']==1" class="overflowOmit">
                  {{arrayConversionCharacter(scope.row[item['value']],item)}}
                </div>
              </template>
          </el-table-column>
        </el-table>
        <!-- 主列表 end -->
        <!-- 分页 start -->
        <div class="pagination">
          <el-pagination
            @current-change="currentChange"
            :current-page.sync="page"
            layout="prev, pager, next, jumper"
            :total="total">
          </el-pagination>
        </div>
        <!-- 分页 end -->
        <!-- 保存 start -->
        <div class="footer">
          <div @click="save()" class="primary-btn mr10">保存</div>
          <div @click="multiSelectBounced.show=false" class="info-btn">取消</div>
        </div>
        <!-- 保存 end -->
      </div>
    </el-dialog>
  </div>
```

#### 2.created生命周期
在created生命周期，需要先转换传入的multiSelectBounced.changeIdsArr，以及将multiSelectBounced.searchData赋值给组件中的变量searchData，并且调用列表数据查询方法。
```javascript
created () {
    this.changeRow = Object.assign([],this.multiSelectBounced.changeIdsArr)
    this.searchData = this.multiSelectBounced.searchData || {}
    this.getList()
}
```

#### 3.方法
```javascript
  methods: {
    // 数组转字符串并去重
    arrayConversionCharacter(arr=[],item) {
      let newArr = [...new Set(arr.map(val => val[item['stringValue']]))]
      return newArr.join(',')
    },
    // 获取成员列表
    getList () {
      this.loading = true
      let {resultList,records} = this.multiSelectBounced.changeArrKey
      // 参数
      let params = Object.assign({
        pageNo:this.page,
        pageSize:10
      },this.searchData)
      // 请求
      let data = {
        method:this.multiSelectBounced.method,
        url:this.multiSelectBounced.listUrl
      }
      if (this.multiSelectBounced.method==='get'||this.multiSelectBounced.method==='GET') {
        data.params = params
      } else {
        data.data = params
      }
      this.$http(data).then((res)=>{
        this.loading = false
        if (res.data.rc === 0) {
          // 总列表
          this.list = res.data.data[resultList]
          if (this.list&&this.list.length>0) {
            this.toggleSelection(this.list)
          }
          // 总条数
          this.total = res.data.data[records]
        }
      }).catch(err => {
        console.log(err)
        this.loading = false
      })
    },
    // 将选中的id打钩
    toggleSelection(list) {
      let id = this.multiSelectBounced.changeArrKey.id
      let changeIdsArr = this.changeRow
      let filterList = list.filter((val)=>{
        return (changeIdsArr.some((val2)=>{
          return val2[id]===val[id]
        }))
      })
      setTimeout(() => {
        filterList.forEach(row => {
          this.$refs.multipleTable.toggleRowSelection(row,true)
        })
      }, 10)
    },
    // 选择页面
    currentChange (val) {
      this.page = val
      this.getList()
    },
    // 查询
    search() {
      this.page = 1
      this.getList()
    },
    // 重置
    reset() {
      for (let index in this.searchData) {
        if (!this.multiSelectBounced.search.some((val)=>{
          return val.isHidden&&(val.value === index)
        })) {
          this.searchData[index]=''
        }
      }
    },
    // 保存
    save() {
      this.$emit('save',this.changeRow)
      this.multiSelectBounced.show = false
    },
    handleSelectionChange(changeValue,row) {
      let changeIdsArr = this.changeRow
      const id = this.multiSelectBounced.changeArrKey.id
      // 判断是点击单选还是全选（row存在是列表单选）
      if (row) {
        let changeIndex = changeIdsArr.findIndex((val)=>{
          return val[id]===row[id]
        })
        if (changeIndex!==-1) {
          // 判断是否是手动选择的去除
          if (changeIndex>=0&&!(changeValue.some((val)=>{
            return val[id]===row[id]
          }))) {
            changeIdsArr.splice(changeIndex,1)
          }
        } else {
          changeIdsArr.push(row)
        }
      } else {
        // 判断是全选还是全不选
        if (changeValue&&changeValue.length>0) {
          changeValue.map((val)=>{
            if (!changeIdsArr.some((val2)=>{
              return val2[id] === val[id]
            })) {
              changeIdsArr.push(val)
            }
          })
        } else {
          this.list.map((val)=>{
            changeIdsArr.splice((changeIdsArr.findIndex((val2)=>{
              return val2[id] === val[id]
            })),1)
          })
        }
      }
    },
    // 切换单选
    radioChange(row) {
      this.changeRow = row
    }
  }
```

### 5.样式
此处采用的是scss语法。
组件内部样式：
```scss
<style lang="scss" scoped>
.multi-select-bounced{
  .multi-select-bounced-btn{
    width: 130px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    height: 40px;
  }
  .pagination{
    text-align: right;
  }
  .footer{
    display: flex;
    margin-top: 10px;
  }
  .overflowOmit{
    overflow: hidden;
    text-overflow:ellipsis;
    white-space: nowrap;
  }
}
</style>
```
修改element-ui全局样式
```scss
<style lang="scss">

```


### 6.调用
+ html中
  ```javascript
  <multiSelect-bounced :multiSelectBounced="checkItemsList" v-if='checkItemsList.show' @save="handleSaveCheckProject"></multiSelect-bounced>
  ```
+ script标签中
  ```javascript
  import multiSelectBounced from '@/components/multiSelectBounced'
  export default {
    components: { multiSelectBounced }
    data() {
      return {
        checkItemsList:{
          show:false,
          listUrl:'/datamanagement/standardindicator/list', // 接口路径
          title:'项目库选择',
          method:'get',
          search:[{
            label:'',
            value:'name',
            placeholder:'请输入项目名称'
          },{
            value:'isDisable',
            isHidden:true
          }],
          searchData:{
            isDisable:false
          },
          tableFields:[{
            label:'项目名称',
            value:'name'
          }],
          changeIdsArr:[],
          changeArrKey:{
            id:'id',
            name:'name',
            resultList:'resultList',
            records:'records'
          }
          // // 单选时的传参
          // checkType: 1,
          // radioValue: ''
        }
      }
    },
    methods: {
      // 保存体检项目
      handleSaveCheckProject(val=[]) {
        this.checkItemsList.changeIdsArr = val
      }
    }
  }
  ```
